    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.讓學生認識全通路行銷的發展趨勢。 <br>2.運用數位科技掌握消費需求發掘創新商機。 <br>3.打造全通路的消費者體驗。 <br>4.強化虛實體通路整合的知識與能力以提升就業力。",
        "en": "1. Let students know The development trend of omni-channel<br>   marketing<br>2. Use digital technology to grasp consumer demand and explore<br>   innovative business opportunities<br>3. Create omni-channel consumer experience<br>4. Strengthen the knowledge and ability of virtual and physical<br>   channel integration to enhance employment."
